{"tid":489241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺上水同大陸已經無分別，不如割讓畀大陸啦屌。","createTime":"2017-12-04T13:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T16:17:46.000Z","uid":27451,"like":9,"dislike":86,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"efc80919269057f77b85898787e6658f99fe36c1","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"d蝗多撚過香港人，成個上水都蝗口蝗面，同大陸有撚分別呀？<br />\n上水中心根撚本就係蝗地㴝，蝗和人的比例係1:10呀屌你。"},{"pid":"09597313f1350d8a42190f3da9d32acf91d41d1a","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d蝗多撚過香港人，成個上水都蝗口蝗面，同大陸有撚分別呀？<br />\n上水中心根撚本就係蝗地㴝，蝗和人的比例係1:10呀屌你。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n10 : 1 先啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1b3c32f38d0beb4b940b5833ba00568f623e26","tid":489241,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:22:51.000Z","msg":"天水圍呢"},{"pid":"8b42c00395527245d1d4987a2690273b4d9922f9","tid":489241,"uid":69083,"like":66,"dislike":3,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:30:30.000Z","msg":"傻撚左呀? 屌你老母臭閪向蝗蟲投降退讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上水係香港人既，做咩撚野要割地而唔撚係諗方法打退班蝗，做咩撚野要鳩縮?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">利申: 鍵盤戰士14lv</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a2676dba697183b532c1edad97e5d2dd645de02","tid":489241,"uid":7262,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:32:11.000Z","msg":"同天水圍一樣 好恐怖既地方"},{"pid":"ff45a323927bfd4b0d7ee88a06ca4fa0049f02ac","tid":489241,"uid":22858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3be43dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3344cbdb4e1010b7e097558ea9dc669d4444205d","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天水圍呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上水多好撚多，10隻有9隻都是蝗㴝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99cafe8f9a6437a2566c92bebac584b1fe47dcf1","tid":489241,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:28:11.000Z","msg":"水泉澳、啟晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db4961c150e9af53dabc57b90f1d08ab4dcecdd9","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>傻撚左呀? 屌你老母臭閪向蝗蟲投降退讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上水係香港人既，做咩撚野要割地而唔撚係諗方法打退班蝗，做咩撚野要鳩縮?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">利申: 鍵盤戰士14lv</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁撚多蝗橫行上水，大撚哂咁係上水鳩鳥鳩行，根本同深圳無撚分別，港豬死撚哂啦。"},{"pid":"dde53448590e525d09c300f9f22a40fcd7112a17","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同天水圍一樣 好恐怖既地方</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每次去親名都，嘩屌佢老母，蝗多撚過羅湖商業城。"},{"pid":"940fcf126f5f843a296c9bf5d63c9165331c1dac","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水泉澳、啟晴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果d係新港蝗，佢老豆係港豬㴝。"},{"pid":"4d92f745d1d1bd4bba7b3f0ce4ff232b71197050","tid":489241,"uid":13586,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:38:24.000Z","msg":"重睇六國論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：上水撚"},{"pid":"9ed14fe34fdfdef3d147e629ce8d0b8ce2f87fe9","tid":489241,"uid":6753,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"你割撚完咪到下個區囉<br />\n到時又割呀？<br />\non9樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d4d92cc9179f74509f7ff1577caaf605e2fe756","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重睇六國論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：上水撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee7d0793b38873b4f57c6b314b536521122dfee","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:41:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你割撚完咪到下個區囉<br />\n到時又割呀？<br />\non9樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n割讓上水，畀撚番香港九龍我地呀屌。"},{"pid":"0a39cadb22eba913917bc683e017037f578134d5","tid":489241,"uid":13586,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>重睇六國論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：上水撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。<br />\n<br />\n智撚障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0085fd4d26f481177d0c391e84ac7cb2d59a1f75","tid":489241,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>重睇六國論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：上水撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。<br />\n<br />\n智撚障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起視四境，而解放軍又至矣。"},{"pid":"18b28fc7edb48a6177b257daef687e1350b5960d","tid":489241,"uid":56107,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:46:08.000Z","m