/>\n燒到眼眉仲未知痛囉！<br />\n阻住你哋返工返學囉！<br />\n<br />\n之後d光復屯門光復沙田光復元朗，上水撚都去幫手，換來嘅係咩呀！<br />\n<br />\n左一句「上水人唔勇武嘅」<br />\n右一句「上水人唔知痛嫁」<br />\n<br />\n上水而家搞就係你呢d自私撚做成嫁！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n火撚滾，唔屌唔舒服！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b0bc687a7374be935cfdede36c62c087f4af8f","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>重睇六國論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：上水撚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日割五城，明日割十城，然後得一夕安寢。<br />\n<br />\n智撚障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9仔，你有無去過上水，有邊忽似香港，狗乜不屌，要㴝做乜鳩？割鳩左去啦。</blockquote><br />\nOn9仔，上水撚呀，喺上水住呀！上水長大上水生活呀，有咩地方比你唔熟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2012年光復上水你條撚樣死咗去邊呀？<br />\n我哋成班上水居民屌到火車站封出口呀，你條撚樣呢？十成十同其他地方一樣食花生啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各家自掃門前雪囉！<br />\n燒到眼眉仲未知痛囉！<br />\n阻住你哋返