normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab452f9a524bba8bdfe1ced6db63007df72448c","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:38:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>文化侵略不嬲都係支那人既特色<br />\n班友最撚鐘意去到邊度就要人地就佢地<br />\n反客為主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就佢老母，d蝗成鳩日要我装微信，我踩鳩佢都傻，其實好多野都係港豬自己做成。"},{"pid":"677df099c91d977482d1e6107ea9d73fac140c21","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中港已經完全融合<br />\n之前星期日/公眾假期嘅反蝗活動根本就係笑話，之後仲要無哂影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c707e55d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090835_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090835_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=663e61b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090844_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090844_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5f67631a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/090852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F090852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e3bc8ef1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n哇痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線，上水呢d蝗地 狗也不屌，割畀蝗係最好方案㴝。</blockquote><br />\n你想割但我唔撚想啊<br />\n我住喺呢度廿幾年點解要我哋犧牲，以前上水人少少落街食嘢都係熟口熟面嘅街坊<br />\n而家睇住啲老字逐間逐間執撚哂，變哂做藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本同住大陸無分別，去撚到上水，蝗口蝗面，見撚到都作嘔呀屌。"},{"pid":"0af23d908ef02baf01dba73570f6afdfb45a9ee9","tid":489241,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d蝗多撚過香港人，成個上水都蝗口蝗面，同大陸有撚分別呀？<br />\n上水中心根撚本就係蝗地㴝，蝗和人的比例係1:10呀屌你。</blockquote><br />\n點解唔成個琛圳割比香港? <br />\n（琛圳人就全部北移）"},{"pid":"9d9f766a3fe99a216e42cf32d94020ea7bac4398","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d蝗多撚過香港人，成個上水都蝗口蝗面，同大陸有撚分別呀？<br />\n上水中心根撚本就係蝗地㴝，蝗和人的比例係1:10呀屌你。</blockquote><br />\n點解唔成個琛圳割比香港? <br />\n（琛圳人就全部北移）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9, 深圳呢d蝗地你要埋我份啦，哂鳩我們港人錢去管理呀。"},{"pid":"3ca994deec8d91d05af00f43093f4ca52c969a97","tid":489241,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"香港啲ibank都請晒支那蝗，你要眼冤的話，割到去中環都仲要割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而全香港好似深水埗最吸引唔到班蝗，但就好多蝻"},{"pid":"aa4d2abb1962407c3d4fb78c1f9bcad0e39dd38a","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港啲ibank都請晒支那蝗，你要眼冤的話，割到去中環都仲要割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而全香港好似深水埗最吸引唔到班蝗，但就好多蝻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁唔割地，有乜方法還我香港原來河山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b6f025e197f07c79d1e5a45a4be74708318315","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ccceae209bd327e24fa7a0147de87d6e94b2adf","tid":489241,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"